<div class="bg-grey-50" id="about">
  <div class="container flex flex-col items-center py-16 md:py-20 lg:flex-row">
    <div class="w-full text-center sm:w-3/4 lg:w-3/5 lg:text-left">
      <h2 class="font-header text-4xl font-semibold uppercase text-primary sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Who am I?
      </h2>
      <h4 class="pt-6 font-header text-xl font-medium text-black sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
        Alexandru-Emil Lupu, Ruby on Rails and Decidim Developer
      </h4>
      <p class="pt-6 font-body leading-relaxed text-grey-20">
        I have more than 20 years experience in the Web Development area, during this time I've mastered a lot of skills,
        from e-commerce platforms implementation and presentation sites, code writing on online games.
        I like to believe about me that I am of the developers who are constantly developing skills,
        and I have no problem to understand Ruby, PHP, Python, JavaScript and Java code.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center pt-6 sm:flex-row lg:justify-start">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start">
          <p class="font-body text-lg font-semibold uppercase text-grey-20">
            Connect with me
          </p>
          <div class="hidden sm:block">
            <i class="bx bx-chevron-right text-2xl text-primary"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center pt-5 pl-2 sm:justify-start sm:pt-0">
          <% data.structure.social.each_with_index do |feat, i| %>
            <a href="<%= feat.url %>" class="pl-4">
              <i class="bx <%= feat.icon %> text-2xl text-primary hover:text-yellow"></i>
            </a>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full pl-0 pt-10 sm:w-3/4 lg:w-2/5 lg:pl-12 lg:pt-0">
      <% data.index.skills.each_with_index do |tech, index| %>
        <div class="<%= index == 0 ? "pt-0" : "pt-6" %>">
          <div class="flex items-end justify-between">
            <h4 class="font-body font-semibold uppercase text-black">
              <%= tech.name %>
            </h4>
            <h3 class="font-body text-3xl font-bold text-primary"><%= tech.percentage %>%</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 h-3 w-full rounded-full bg-lila">
            <div class="h-3 rounded-full bg-primary" style="width: <%=tech.percentage %>%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>